{"tid":389801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Dr.Jim] 歲月神偷 - 高登開站文獻","createTime":"2017-09-06T14:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T12:05:49.000Z","uid":52127,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6bcd4cff1a7576252e7c7ac90d8ac480067eae98","tid":389801,"uid":52127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:32:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://drjimdiary.blogspot.hk/2017/09/blog-post.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdrjimdiary.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F09%2Fblog-post.html&d=uWhpOTAvkXPwREn6UIw4dARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e713a27f\" target=\"_blank\">http://drjimdiary.blogspot.hk/2017/09/blog-post.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oDAPjQJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoDAPjQJ.jpg&h=f5b31678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上個月其中一位高登的舊拍檔陳先生搵我，告訴我他的 Office 要搬了，問我一些封塵已久的高登舊的文件還要不要保留。我說不如先給我看一下吧，其中一些文件可能有紀念價值。<br />\n<br />\n翻開這此舊文件，都已經是15、16年前的往事了。回憶都是美好的，但是也沒必要老是把舊東西儲下來，所以最後決定把文件丟掉前拍了一些照片給大家分享：<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-lwoDJN3TlEw/Wa6ky3YLX4I/AAAAAAAAAcM/xlGnmXodWRM1WLs0Hhn6GsIdaa4E7-fMwCLcBGAs/s1600/IMG_5044.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-lwoDJN3TlEw%2FWa6ky3YLX4I%2FAAAAAAAAAcM%2FxlGnmXodWRM1WLs0Hhn6GsIdaa4E7-fMwCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FIMG_5044.JPG&h=a4dae5d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-STt3n6xvieo/Wa6ky6j_nUI/AAAAAAAAAcQ/oOdOFZZZ2mQe0ZbpLJA_D2C7PelUAIWkQCLcBGAs/s1600/IMG_5045.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-STt3n6xvieo%2FWa6ky6j_nUI%2FAAAAAAAAAcQ%2FoOdOFZZZ2mQe0ZbpLJA_D2C7PelUAIWkQCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FIMG_5045.JPG&h=dd7d1ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這兩份銀行月結單，見證了當時高登會員的熱誠和支持。當時網上銀行和電子支付還未流行，但是每天都有不少網友願意花$38/88通過ATM過數給我們做高級會員。感激！"},{"pid":"c3a2a93d87fc771e6fb32fc1ab744d01274b0acf","tid":389801,"uid":52127,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3KjG2JPd9vk/Wa6kzo5CeiI/AAAAAAAAAcY/4VfBbhQWLV80O61qeaCpkn1unYVFvH4bACLcBGAs/s1600/IMG_5047.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-3KjG2JPd9vk%2FWa6kzo5CeiI%2FAAAAAAAAAcY%2F4VfBbhQWLV80O61qeaCpkn1unYVFvH4bACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FIMG_5047.JPG&h=6d694a7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時PIII 1G PC要萬幾元一部<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-6Dq2KrstPpo/Wa6kz1N__LI/AAAAAAAAAcc/ag4Dj0sbZY0JvdP5KbHtlaG9N0RpY3gAwCLcBGAs/s1600/IMG_5048.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-6Dq2KrstPpo%2FWa6kz1N__LI%2FAAAAAAAAAcc%2Fag4Dj0sbZY0JvdP5KbHtlaG9N0RpY3gAwCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FIMG_5048.JPG&h=9ac2d611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時的版面設計和「膳稿」<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Gq49jmqnbp8/Wa6kz4Wmt3I/AAAAAAAAAcg/RvnVTsLUya4-gEbiLxTVYPXxw66IyqfqgCLcBGAs/s1600/IMG_5049.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Gq49jmqnbp8%2FWa6kz4Wmt3I%2FAAAAAAAAAcg%2FRvnVTsLUya4-gEbiLxTVYPXxw66IyqfqgCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FIMG_5049.JPG&h=c0edf8c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開站時的宣傳稿，當時每日瀏覽人數有1,000人 :-) 現在有 1,000萬了吧!?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-CsWVp-d81Fg/Wa6k0aW7y9I/AAAAAAAAAck/pGt23zjhuO8cdq6B0WDXTw0GUiEkh21EgCLcBGAs/s1600/IMG_5052.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-CsWVp-d81Fg%2FWa6k0aW7y9I%2FAAAAAAAAAck%2FpGt23zjhuO8cdq6B0WDXTw0GUiEkh21EgCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FIMG_5052.JPG&h=ce6d4c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾幾何時，我們也曾經賣過音效卡和小喇叭，最後當然是失敗最終<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-i4x2TU3khz0/Wa6rqtk08wI/AAAAAAAAAc4/BdO3oYvd_uIdiT7khDesEJcoZQ7Udx77QCLcBGAs/s1600/post_asp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-i4x2TU3khz0%2FWa6rqtk08wI%2FAAAAAAAAAc4%2FBdO3oYvd_uIdiT7khDesEJcoZQ7Udx77QCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fpost_asp.png&h=dd0a977f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部份ASP原碼<br />\n<br />\n當時成立高登除了為興趣外，有兩個主要目標：1) 不要虧本 ; 2)高登文化要存承下去。今天回顧，兩個目標均已經達到。而上面的文件，當是歷史的一部份吧。"},{"pid":"8b23bcd689f3b6bf4b48bdfaba1a2e2a2004c1c2","tid":389801,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6197708b8608bbb3af05d95a8fd66fd0ef6f40","tid":389801,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:07:59.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"369c90f7f025559650b36423b8e3094ebbe250a6","tid":389801,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:14:45.000Z","msg":"none watch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4891dc3e7571ed56bef84e08a91d3c0cbfd431","tid":389801,"uid":52127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:43:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>none watch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=BW&amp;message=6780765&amp;page=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DBW%26message%3D6780765%26page%3D2&d=uWhpOTAvkXPwREn6UIw4dARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=5c7ee96f\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=BW&amp;message=6780765&amp;page=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23ab796ba68b341444389350a92bb94c22d6d9f","tid":389801,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>none watch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n魔魔有冇睇到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63bb4340f730fb80cd63631edfcd726acbbcd6e6","tid":389801,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:58:12.000Z","msg":"當年廿幾歲<br />\n